{"id": "art-574", "label": "Art. 574", "title": "Art. 574: Executarea confiscării speciale şi a confiscării extinse", "slug": "art-574", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_245103337\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1140\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_245103337\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 574:\nExecutarea confisc&#259;rii speciale &#351;i a confisc&#259;rii extinse </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1888051215\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1139\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1888051215\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>M&#259;sura de siguran&#355;&#259; a confisc&#259;rii\nspeciale sau a confisc&#259;rii extinse, luat&#259; prin hot&#259;rârea\ninstan&#355;ei de judecat&#259;, se execut&#259; dup&#259; cum urmeaz&#259;:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2109176083\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1138\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2109176083\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)lucrurile confiscate se predau organelor în drept a le\nprelua sau valorifica potrivit legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_685716372\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1137\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_685716372\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)dac&#259; lucrurile confiscate se afl&#259; în\np&#259;strarea organelor de poli&#355;ie sau a altor institu&#355;ii,\njudec&#259;torul delegat cu executarea trimite o copie de pe dispozitivul\nhot&#259;rârii organului la care se afl&#259;. Dup&#259; primirea copiei de pe\ndispozitiv, lucrurile confiscate se predau organelor în drept a le prelua sau\nvalorifica potrivit dispozi&#355;iilor legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1750192593\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1136\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1750192593\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)atunci când confiscarea prive&#351;te sume de bani ce nu\nau fost consemnate la unit&#259;&#355;i bancare, judec&#259;torul delegat cu\nexecutarea trimite o copie de pe dispozitivul hot&#259;rârii organelor fiscale,\nîn vederea execut&#259;rii confisc&#259;rii potrivit dispozi&#355;iilor privind\ncrean&#355;ele bugetare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1331237094\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1135\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1331237094\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)când s-a dispus distrugerea lucrurilor confiscate,\naceasta se face în prezen&#355;a judec&#259;torului delegat cu executarea,\nîntocmindu-se proces-verbal care se depune la dosarul cauzei.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 4:Punerea în executare a altor\ndispozi&#355;ii</span></b></p>"}